HATTERAS HOUSE offers a simple and relaxing place to stay steps from the surf. Ground level provides all weather entry, 2 carports, 2 outdoor showers, ping pong, hammock and lighted fish station with hot/cold water. The first level features a large bedroom with flat screen TV, full bath, laundry room, den with wet bar, TV, pull out couch and hot tub on screened porch.
